    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238220/extras/3ce36f1fe6309fca269fa1fcd9ea959e.poster.avif?t=1770631024\" width=1170 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238220/extras/3ce36f1fe6309fca269fa1fcd9ea959e.webm?t=1770631024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238220/extras/3ce36f1fe6309fca269fa1fcd9ea959e.mp4?t=1770631024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >六角之手》是一款卡组建造和塔防游戏，您要利用具有疯狂攻击模式的塔楼，通过建造致命迷宫来控制敌人的行进路线。用奇异的塔楼和魔法咒语打造完美的卡组，增强防御力或杀死敌人！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238220/extras/da21656220ad84084d748c7c1a8d91b3.poster.avif?t=1770631024\" width=1000 height=2000 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238220/extras/da21656220ad84084d748c7c1a8d91b3.webm?t=1770631024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238220/extras/da21656220ad84084d748c7c1a8d91b3.mp4?t=1770631024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238220/extras/ea1612dcc34fe2a95ee71e7f5bdcef28.avif?t=1770631024\" width=616 height=104 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238220/extras/0d846e098a61951da9ca515ef81b187e.poster.avif?t=1770631024\" width=780 height=412 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238220/extras/0d846e098a61951da9ca515ef81b187e.webm?t=1770631024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238220/extras/0d846e098a61951da9ca515ef81b187e.mp4?t=1770631024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次运行都是独一无二的，有不同的卡组、遭遇和关卡</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有文字，也没有说明--通过尝试和错误找出每个塔和咒语的作用</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿越三张程序地图--再来一次，难度更大</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238220/extras/761a9f716444aebad168b93e7ce660f0.avif?t=1770631024\" width=616 height=104 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238220/extras/84338f9561be222895e6aaf3a2aa7fff.poster.avif?t=1770631024\" width=780 height=410 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238220/extras/84338f9561be222895e6aaf3a2aa7fff.webm?t=1770631024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238220/extras/84338f9561be222895e6aaf3a2aa7fff.mp4?t=1770631024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《方块之手》中，塔楼拥有独特的攻击模式：它们可能只向一个方向射击，也可能绕射或发射猛烈的蜜蜂。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >定位你的塔楼，引导敌人穿越致命迷宫</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过法术卡为塔楼加持</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238220/extras/d250eb831e542eb28a6d7443f093358b.avif?t=1770631024\" width=616 height=150 /></span></p></li></ul>",
